ation.\nThe conclusions obtained in this work can yield useful guidelines for\nsubsequent quantum switch designs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 2 Dec 2022 21:55:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-06"}
